title: Montenegro Average Monthly Wages in Manufacturing
description: Wages in Manufacturing in Montenegro increased to 718 EUR/Month in September from 717 EUR/Month in August of 2022. Wages in Manufacturing in Montenegro averaged 654.96 EUR/Month from 2011 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 827 EUR/Month in June of 2012 and a record low of 568 EUR/Month in August of 2021. This page provides - Montenegro Average Monthly Wages in Manufacturing- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistical Office of Montenegro
